 addressing emerging environmental economic and security threats around the world if you d like to make your gift online using credit card please go to giving to fsi stanford to designate fsi or one of the centers or programs here please select other on the first pull down menu then on the second page further designation you may type fsi or one of the centers or programs in the special instructions further designation box gifts to fsi are tax deductible under applicable rules the institute is part of stanford university's tax exempt status as a section 501 c 3 public charity giving opportunities center priorities giving opportunities fsi centers and programs search more information neil penick associate director for development and external relations support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 9632 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
